          {
            "text": "Katy, Texas, has a high density of top-tier medical spas. Depending on whether you are looking for advanced injectables, medical weight loss, or high-end facials, different locations stand out.\n\nBased on recent rankings, patient reviews, and service specializations for 2024–2025, here are the best medspas in Katy:\n\n### 1. **Katy Med Tech Spa** (Best for Skin Rejuvenation & Overall Rating)\nThis is currently one of the highest-rated medspas in the area, boasting over 1,000 five-star reviews. They are particularly well-known for their personalized approach to facials and laser treatments.\n*   **Best for:** Signature facials, laser hair removal, and body contouring.\n*   **Known for:** Excellent first-time customer deals (e.g., Ageless Signature Facials for ~$60) and a high focus on customer service.\n\n### 2. **Viata Aesthetics and Wellness** (Best for Injectables & Weight Loss)\nViata is frequently cited for its expertise in \"liquid facelifts\" and medical wellness. It is a top choice if you want a provider who specializes in facial sculpting rather than just basic \"unit-based\" Botox.\n*   **Best for:** Botox/Dysport, dermal fillers (lips and cheeks), and medically supervised weight loss (Semaglutide/Tirzepatide).\n*   **Known for:** Lead injector Candace is highly praised for creating natural-looking results and tailored beauty plans.\n\n### 3. **Luxe Medical Aesthetics** (Best for Luxury & Facials)\nLocated on Kingsland Blvd, Luxe has earned a reputation for being the \"Best of Katy\" in local polls. They offer a high-end boutique environment and medical-grade skincare that focuses on long-term skin health.\n*   **Best for:** DiamondGlow facials, VI Peels, and hair restoration.\n*   **Known for:** Exceptional hospitality and staff expertise (specifically Sana for facials). They also frequently offer BOGO deals on laser treatments.\n\n### 4. **MedSpa At Villagio** (Best \"One-Stop Shop\")\nA two-time winner of the \"Medspa of the Year\" award by Image Skincare, this location combines a traditional day spa feel with advanced medical treatments.\n*   **Best for:** A mix of relaxation and results. They offer everything from laser skin resurfacing and fat reduction to traditional massages and salon services.\n*   **Known for:** Having over 15 years of experience and a team of board-certified physicians on-site.\n\n### 5. **SkinSpirit Katy** (Best for Clinical Excellence)\nSkinSpirit is a nationally recognized brand that recently expanded to Katy. They are known for hiring highly trained medical professionals (RNs and PAs) who prioritize safety and medically-proven results.\n*   **Best for:** Advanced injectables, microneedling, and clinical-grade chemical peels.\n*   **Known for:** Natural transformations. It’s a great choice if you prefer a more clinical, data-driven environment.\n\n### 6. **Legacy Med Spa** (Best for Holistic Wellness)\nIf you are looking for \"beauty from the inside out,\" Legacy is a strong contender. They focus heavily on wellness services alongside traditional aesthetics.\n*   **Best for:** IV Hydration therapy, custom facials, and \"naturally refined\" Botox results.\n*   **Known for:** A tranquil, \"sanctuary\" vibe and a focus on whole-body wellness.\n\n---\n\n### **Quick Tips for Choosing:**\n*   **For First-Timers:** Look for **Katy Med Tech Spa** or **Luxe**; they are known for their thorough consultations and \"no-pressure\" environments.\n*   **For Mature Skin:** **Viata Aesthetics** or **SkinSpirit** are better for deeper anti-aging needs like fillers and structural skin tightening.\n*   **Check for Specials:** Many Katy medspas (like **Luminous MediSpa**) offer significant discounts for new patients or monthly memberships that can save you 15-20% on maintenance treatments.",
            "thoughtSignature": ""
          }
        ],
        "role": "model"
      },
